# KH Rights Finder – Evidence-first

## Data sourcing & scoring

- Cambodia authoritative sources are **Tier A** and the only drivers of verdict/risk scoring.
- Never infer missing fields. If a value is not present in the source or snapshot, set it to `null` and append an entry to `parse_warnings`.

## Auditability

- Always persist `raw_text` plus a saved snapshot reference so every extracted fact can be traced back to its source.

## Workflow hygiene

- **One task per chat.** If asked for backend-only work, do not touch frontend files (and vice versa).

## Testing & migrations

- Include tests for any backend logic changes.
- Include an Alembic migration for any DB schema changes.
